title: 23 WAYS TO HAVE FUN AT HOME || APRIL FOOLS' DAY PRANKS
description:
Hilarious pranks for everyone at home

In this video, I show you how to make the best of April fools with these amazing prank ideas you should try. 
You can start your day by drawing a spider on the toilet paper in your bathroom. Anyone who’s terrified of spiders won’t even step in. 
You can also offer your friends some strawberries, but beforehand make sure you remove some of the fruit in the middle and fill it up with ginger or garlic.
You can also apply nail polish on a clean soap bar and put it in the bathroom. Nobody would be able to wash their hands with it. 
Another great idea is to dip Brussel sprouts in some chocolate sauce and serve them to your friend. 
You can also take an oreo cookie, remove the cream from the middle and replace it with toothpaste. 
Another fun idea is to open a bag of crisps and coat the top of it with Nutella. Then offer some crisps to your friends and watch their reaction. 

#StayAtHome
